kipedia.org/wiki/Interoperability\">inter-operable formats</a></li>","updatedAt":"2015-04-13T19:35:24.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>What is an open company?</h2>","itemHTML":"<li>developing its products openly, using public communication channels</li>","updatedAt":"2015-04-13T19:35:24.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>What is an open company?</h2>","itemHTML":"<li>publishing as much financial and operational data as possible, without compromising customer privacy.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-04-13T19:35:24.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>What is an open company?</h2>","itemHTML":"<li>etc.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-04-13T19:35:24.000Z"}]},"previous":{"id":"awesomes/github.com/szenergy/awesome-lidar","repo":"szenergy/awesome-lidar"},"next":{"id":"awesomes/github.com/mmccaff/PlacesToPostYourStartup","repo":"mmccaff/PlacesToPostYourStartup"}},"pageContext":{"type":"week","repo":"opencompany/awesome-open-company","id":"awesomes/github.com/opencompany/awesome-open-company","previousId":"awesomes/github.com/szenergy/awesome-lidar","nextId":"awesomes/github.com/mmccaff/PlacesToPostYourStartup"}},"staticQueryHashes":["228695001","2744905544","3289010534"]}